data.description: Welcome to 5941 Coral Way! This charming single-family home is situated in the heart of Miami and features a 3 bedroom/2 Bath set up with 1,043ft² of living space on a generous 3,903ft² lot. The property also offers a bonus den and side/back patio spaces, offering the perfect blend of comfort and space for a variety of lifestyles. Convenience is key with this property, as it sits near excellent schools, parks, and popular shopping centers. Centrally located between the vibrant neighborhoods of Coral Gables and West Miami, this home offers easy access to major highways and is only a short 15-minute drive to FIU and MIA. Don't miss the opportunity to make this centrally situated gem your new home! Schedule a viewing today! Needs very little TLC to make it perfect!
